{"tid":1995353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍第7艦隊：中國主權擴張威脅海上自由 將繼續於南海執行任務以展示軍權","createTime":"2020-04-30T07:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T08:43:03.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e624b437dbcde67c4eb5ad14b8ab9e2d068549d2","tid":1995353,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"美軍艦連續2日到中國控制南海島礁近海游弋<br />\n30.04.2020 15:36<br />\n<br />\n美軍軍艦連續兩日到中國控制的南海島礁近海，執行所謂的&ldquo;航行自由任務&rdquo;；美軍第7艦隊發言人說，&ldquo;邦克山號&rdquo;導彈巡洋艦昨日在南薰礁近海通過，指中國對南海提出主權主張，為海上自由帶來嚴峻威脅，美軍將繼續執行有關任務。<br />\n<br />\n美軍&ldquo;巴里號&rdquo;導彈驅逐艦，前日在中國控制的西沙群島周邊游弋，中國軍方指責美軍侵犯領海。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284392&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284392%26csid%3D261_341&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=f56460d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284392&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"eefd5830ae7ccb2ac0ba6da178cece1c1e405a9a","tid":1995353,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"自己領海都俾人自出自入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9000418c8c43a879bb897ea97b971cd69ec5def","tid":1995353,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"駐軍台灣！"},{"pid":"33d4431d76877d2e3ca502110a6ef0b3636f3316","tid":1995353,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9000418c8c43a879bb897ea97b971cd69ec5def","tid":1995353,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"駐軍台灣！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/su